      "full_body_preview": "The 24-hour bakeoff loop is alive on a userspace daemon after launchd refused to cooperate, and it's already producing agents faster than it can lint them.\n\n## What shipped\n\n- `4f3b7de6d` swapped the broken launchd plist for a userspace daemon. The launchd path failed silently — no logs, no ticks, no errors — which is exactly the worst failure mode. The userspace daemon at least crashes loudly.\n- `f55663960` finally taught git to ignore the runtime litter: `continuum.pid`, `continuum.log`, `cont"
